high_descs: Turn right to face the wall.
Pick up the tennis racket from the floor.
Turn left, then left again to go to the nightstand next to the bed.
Put the racket on the nightstand
anns.task_desc: Put the tennis racket on the nightstand.

high_descs: Turn 90 degrees to your right and look down at the floor.
Pick up the racquet from the floor in the corner.
Turn to your left and go counterclockwise around the room until you come to the nightstand at the right of the bed.
Stand the racquet upright on its handle against the wall, just left of the center of the back of the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Prop a racquet against the wall on top of a nightstand.

high_descs: Turn to the right and look at the floor.
Take the tennis racket that is on the floor next to the baseball bat.
Turn around and walk across the room to the table on the right side of the bed.
Place the tennis racket behind the keys on the bedside table.
anns.task_desc: To place the racket on the table.
